Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.57,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之使者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:04.86,Black,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Cure Black
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.77,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の使者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.77,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之使者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.33,White,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\bord5\b0\be5}Cure White
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.20,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ふたりはプリキュア！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.20,Default CN,,0,0,0,,我们两人是Precure！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.84,Default JP,,0,0,0,,闇の力の僕たちよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.84,Default CN,,0,0,0,,黑暗力量的奴仆们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.12,Default JP,,0,0,0,,とっととお家に  帰りなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:19.12,Default CN,,0,0,0,,还不快点给我滚回老家去！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:26.40,Hikari,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\b0}Luminous Shining Stream
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.27,Default JP,,0,0,0,,輝く命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.10,0:14:51.27,Default CN,,0,0,0,,闪耀的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.97,Hikari,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5\b0}Shiny Luminous
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.97,Default JP,,0,0,0,,光の心と光の意志
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.80,0:14:56.97,Default CN,,0,0,0,,光之心与光之意志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.45,Default JP,,0,0,0,,全てをひとつにするために！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.45,Default CN,,0,0,0,,让一切合而为一吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.92,Monster JP,,0,0,0,,ザケンナー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.92,Monster CN,,0,0,0,,搞事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:29.92,Default JP,,0,0,0,,どんなに力尽くで  私達の未来を潰そうとしても...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.97,0:15:29.92,Default CN,,0,0,0,,无论你们怎样费心费力地想要破坏我们的未来...
