Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.52,0:18:03.55,Default CN,,0,0,0,,是火上浇“油”才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.30,Default JP,,0,0,0,,ルミナス！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:05.30,Default CN,,0,0,0,,Luminous！
